 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003ESocialNotions, Inc. is a Los Angeles based company that provides social marketing technology and services to brands and filmmakers. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThey specialize in innovative social marketing strategies and helping companies figure out what they should be doing with social media. They are also in the process of developing a tool called Rippl which serves to trigger and facilitate conversations between \u0026#8220;who we are and the things we buy\u0026#8221;. Rippl is based on the combination of web semantics, social commerce and social/mobile consumer apps. The Beta release and first live customer are expected in Q1 2010.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EIn addition, the company also provides marketing engineering services for the purpose of consumer segmentation and targeting, media planning, customer value assessment and diffusion modeling.\u003C/p\u003E",
